   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Ninety-six THE LORD S BLOOD CLEANSES US FROM SIN Scripture: 1 John 1:7 The Lord Jesus bore our sins on the cross and shed His blood for us The function of the Lord s blood Because Jesus bore our sins and shed His blood, His blood can cleanse us from our sins.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>The cleansing of the Lord s blood is always effective.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>The meaning of being cleansed from sins The Lord s blood cleanses us from our sins; that is, it erases our record of sins before God.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>When we are cleansed by the Lord s blood, all record of our sins is erased before God.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>How to obtain the cleansing of the Lord s blood</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Develop this point.</S>
